snippet.title: Super Mario 127 - F3 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario 127 is an official sequel to the critically acclaimed 2009 fangame Super Mario 63. SM127 aims to capture the charm of its predecessor, while also providing a new experience with improved gameplay, level designer, and an entirely new campaign! 

Try out the newest version "0.8.0: the Galaxy Update" today!

Join the official discord for live updates of SM127: https://discord.gg/mario-127 or https://discord.gg/h7rABhRtvv

Check out the itch.io page for SM127 to download the 0.8.0 update: https://charpurrr.itch.io/super-mario-127
